- Follow standard Phoenix project structure conventions.
- Contexts belong in `lib/app_name/`.
- Web layer components belong in `lib/app_name_web/`.
- Tests should mirror the lib structure in `test/`.
- Static assets belong in `assets/`.
- Translation files are in `priv/gettext/` (if using internationalization).
- Plans and documentation go in `codegen/plans/`.
